    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>meat-free mince</strong>,<strong> grated ginger</strong>,<strong> soy sauce </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>in a bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> meat-free mince meatball mix</strong></p>",
